            <div class="col-12 col-md-10">
                <p><p> 
                    Overall, learning to cook my mom's recipes taught me that the "second shift" is often taken for granted. She never failed to cook us meals every day after working as a housekeeper. This process has made me appreciate her even more than I thought possible. She is truly an inspiration and a powerhouse of a woman. If interested in more in-depth recipes- feel free to reach me via Instagram or Twitter @ufosteph.</p>
